{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Create a full-width hero section in a clean, modern style similar to tentree.com. Use a soft beige/neutral background, max-width container centered, and a two-column layout: text on the left, image on the right. Add this H1 exactly once: “Premium Wall Art & Professional UV Printing Services”. Add a short paragraph about shopping wall art or booking same-day UV printing from our Noida studio. Add two pill-shaped buttons side by side: “Shop By Category” linking to #shop-by-category and “Book Services” linking to #book-services. The right image should be large, with rounded corners and a soft shadow. On mobile, stack text above image with generous padding., Under the hero, create a new section with id="shop-by-category" in the same visual style as the hero and tentree.com. Use a soft neutral background and a centered max-width container. Add an H2: “Shop Premium Wall Art by Category” and a short paragraph. Below, create 3 pill-style tabs: Paintings, Metal Posters, Acrylic Posters. Each tab should show a horizontally scrollable row of product cards from a collection picker. Each card: rounded white card, soft shadow, product image on top, product title as H3, small meta line, and a full-width pill “Buy Now” button linking to the product URL. Only one tab’s cards are visible at a time. Match spacing, rounded corners and hover feel to tentree-style product rows.
{% enddoc %}
